name: INTERNATIONAL TRASHART FIGHT
description:
Joint project in collaboration with the artist @Ftrsaroth (Mexico) and XeldaJara (Argentina).
This fight consists of a photograph of the container of each country, (or city or state) to be intervened by the opposite. This time MEXICO-ARGENTINA. We accept new challenges. (Has Sound by Ftrsarot) 1440 x 1080 pixels.
